WEBVTT

00:02.611 --> 00:04.830
[woman on TV]
'A baby is the beginning
of all things'

00:04.917 --> 00:08.747
'and the most beautiful
experience a woman can have.'

00:08.834 --> 00:10.880
'It's a time of wonder'

00:10.967 --> 00:14.231
'celebrating
the miracle of nature.'

00:14.318 --> 00:15.754
What you watching, Mol?

00:15.841 --> 00:19.236
Oh, a documentary on,
uh, natural childbirth

00:19.323 --> 00:20.455
when I do finally get pregnant

00:20.542 --> 00:22.109
I want to know
what all my options are.

00:22.196 --> 00:23.762
Well, I'm gonna do it
the old-fashioned way

00:23.849 --> 00:25.068
loaded on painkillers,
screaming

00:25.155 --> 00:27.070
"Get this thing out of me!"

00:27.157 --> 00:28.985
Well, that's always
a fallback, but..

00:29.072 --> 00:32.249
I'm actually curious about
this underwater birthing.

00:32.336 --> 00:34.686
Oh, that's why
she's squatting naked

00:34.773 --> 00:36.949
in that swimming pool.

00:37.037 --> 00:38.690
Correct. Yeah.

00:38.777 --> 00:40.823
They say that the warm water
helps relax you

00:40.910 --> 00:42.520
and, you know, makes for a..

00:42.607 --> 00:44.740
...a less traumatic
transition for the baby.

00:44.827 --> 00:46.959
Sure. I guess, as long as
all the other people

00:47.047 --> 00:49.527
at the pool don't mind.

00:49.614 --> 00:51.573
No, you're not doing it
at the Y.

00:51.660 --> 00:53.270
They won't even let you swim
without a cap..

00:53.357 --> 00:56.534
[gasps]
Oh, she's going into labor.

00:56.621 --> 00:57.840
This is so beautiful.

00:57.927 --> 00:59.755
I think I'm getting
a little choked up.

00:59.842 --> 01:01.670
Right.
This really is a miracle.

01:01.757 --> 01:04.368
[woman screaming on TV]

01:04.455 --> 01:06.414
- Oh, God!
- Here it comes!

01:06.501 --> 01:10.244
[woman on TV]
'Finally, the baby
is released gently'

01:10.331 --> 01:12.333
'into the warm water.'

01:12.420 --> 01:14.030
- God!
- Oh, my God!

01:14.117 --> 01:15.901
- Oh, God!
- What are you watching?

01:15.988 --> 01:18.121
Is it shark week again?

01:18.208 --> 01:21.255
No, it's a video
of natural childbirth.

01:21.342 --> 01:23.300
That's horrifying!
Thanks a lot.

01:23.387 --> 01:25.868
I was just going to the kitchen
to get something to eat.

01:25.955 --> 01:27.217
What are you doing now?

01:27.304 --> 01:30.090
Going to the kitchen
to get something to eat.

01:30.177 --> 01:32.570
Forget this. Just pump me
full of drugs and booze.

01:32.657 --> 01:34.442
Done and done.

01:34.529 --> 01:36.661
Oh, my god, she's biting
through the umbilical cord!

01:36.748 --> 01:40.709
Yuck! It's like watching
mike eat calamari.

01:40.796 --> 01:42.667
Seriously, just give me
a spine full of morphine

01:42.754 --> 01:44.974
and a bellyful of hooch,
I want that baby coming out

01:45.061 --> 01:47.455
pie-eyed and singing
"Danny Boy."

01:47.542 --> 01:52.938
♪ For the first time
in my life ♪

01:53.025 --> 01:56.812
♪ I see love ♪♪

02:07.910 --> 02:11.000
So, you and molly got any
big plans for Valentine's Day?

02:11.087 --> 02:12.915
