and then baby sex

02:13.002 --> 02:15.135
which is just like regular sex
but with half the passion

02:15.222 --> 02:17.876
and twice the worry.

02:17.963 --> 02:19.269
It's still sex, though.

02:19.356 --> 02:20.662
I didn't say bad,
just different.

02:20.749 --> 02:23.665
Like pineapple on pizza.

02:23.752 --> 02:26.015
Since I don't have a special
lady in my life this year

02:26.102 --> 02:27.451
I'm just gonna lay low.

02:27.538 --> 02:29.105
