they might as well jump on me.

02:36.504 --> 02:37.461
And pardon me
for caring about ladies

02:37.548 --> 02:38.810
going through a rough patch.

02:38.897 --> 02:40.203
Yeah, you're quite
the humanitarian

02:40.290 --> 02:43.424
always willing to lend
a helping penis.

02:43.511 --> 02:45.643
Say whatever you want but
I've cleaned up my act a lot.

02:45.730 --> 02:50.082
It's been a long time since
I've trolled for bus-pass ass.

02:50.170 --> 02:52.476
