incident" of '08.

02:52.563 --> 02:54.043
[laughs]

02:54.130 --> 02:57.307
You spent the whole night
crying and gargling.

02:59.353 --> 03:01.833
Learned a lot of lessons
that night.

03:01.920 --> 03:03.487
Which I'm gonna
pass on to Samuel.

03:03.574 --> 03:05.924
That boy is desperate
for an experienced mentor.

03:06.011 --> 03:07.926
