05:03.259 --> 05:07.611
But it did help me lose what
is now a total of 40 pounds.

05:07.698 --> 05:10.005
Did he really crack
the big 4-0?

05:10.092 --> 05:11.398
Actually, thirty-eight
and a half

05:11.485 --> 05:13.878
but I'm gonna let him
have his moment.

05:13.965 --> 05:15.184
But I didn't come here to brag.

05:15.271 --> 05:17.578
Yes, he did.

05:17.665 --> 05:19.884
I'm just here
to inspire and encourage

05:19.971 --> 05:21.973
because if I can do it,
you can do it.

05:22.060 --> 05:24.585
All it takes is submitting
to this simple program

05:24.672 --> 05:26.151
and being married
to a wonderful woman

05:26.238 --> 05:29.372
who will actually
slap pizza out of your hand.

05:29.459 --> 05:32.593
Truthfully, I had to tear it out
of his teeth.

05:32.680 --> 05:35.509
Yeah, it's like getting
a sock away from a dog.

05:35.596 --> 05:37.989
Alright, I think we have time
for one more share.

05:38.076 --> 05:39.643
I better get
this over with.

05:39.730 --> 05:41.645
Walk of shame...
I'm up four pounds.

05:41.732 --> 05:45.345
- Stay strong.
- We can't all be winners.

05:45.432 --> 05:48.086
Hi. My name is Harry,
and I am an over-eater.

05:48.173 --> 05:49.218
[all]
Hi, harry.

05:49.305 --> 05:50.959
I had a rather tumultuous week

05:51.046 --> 05:55.267
