- This is depressing.

05:56.965 --> 05:58.358
You want to get out of here?

05:58.445 --> 06:00.882
It's a support group.
He sat through yours.

06:00.969 --> 06:04.320
But mine was inspiring.
I gave these people a hero.

06:04.407 --> 06:07.323
Valentine's day is a particular
trigger for me.

06:07.410 --> 06:10.587
For, on that fateful day,
I gave my heart

06:10.674 --> 06:12.937
to the love of my life

06:13.024 --> 06:16.767
'only to have her crush it
like an empty slim-fast can.'

06:16.854 --> 06:19.770
Which she could do...
on her forehead, even.

06:19.857 --> 06:21.598
'God, I loved that woman.'

06:21.685 --> 06:25.254
