all the single women

07:52.907 --> 07:54.125
right here in Chicago?

07:54.212 --> 07:55.518
Well, I think
the language barrier

07:55.605 --> 07:57.172
would really play in his favor.

07:57.259 --> 07:59.653
Vietnamese girl,
maybe Cambodian..

07:59.740 --> 08:02.177
Any of your war-ravaged
countries.

08:05.397 --> 08:06.964
I think it's a horrible idea

08:07.051 --> 08:08.618
fixing your sister up
with Harry.

08:08.705 --> 08:11.142
Why not? They're both
available, lovely people.

08:11.229 --> 08:12.753
Yeah, but this
isn't a fairy tale.

08:12.840 --> 08:14.276
The troll doesn't get
the princess.

08:14.363 --> 08:17.105
He stays under the bridge
with his riddles.

08:17.192 --> 08:19.281
Look, if she got to know
the guy I saw tonight

08:19.368 --> 08:20.848
she could look past
all the other..

08:20.935 --> 08:23.633
- Atrocities?
- Quirks. Okay?

08:23.720 --> 08:25.983
He's a very sweet soul,
and so is Victoria.

08:26.070 --> 08:28.769
Victoria is a show pony,
Harry is a three-legged mule

08:28.856 --> 08:30.597
with an ass
covered in flies.

08:30.684 --> 08:32.773
