is a three-legged mule.

08:35.079 --> 08:36.690
Are we making
three-legged mules?

08:36.777 --> 08:40.128
Because I think we're out of
grapefruit juice and grenadine.

08:40.215 --> 08:43.871
See? There's already kind of
a language barrier built in.

08:43.958 --> 08:45.829
Victoria, you don't want
to go out with Harry, do you?

08:45.916 --> 08:48.266
Mike, that's not how we do it,
you ease into it.

08:48.353 --> 08:49.572
Who's Harry?
Are we done here?

08:49.659 --> 08:51.182
Okay, alright.

08:51.269 --> 08:54.925
He is a really nice guy
that we know from OA.

08:55.012 --> 08:58.668
And he's been over
here several times.

08:58.755 --> 09:01.192
