at Christmas.

09:01.279 --> 09:03.455
Oh, the chunky guy
with the sweater vest

09:03.543 --> 09:05.153
and matronly upper arms?

09:05.240 --> 09:07.677
Oh, you noticed his arms.

09:07.764 --> 09:10.680
Well, turns out,
he is currently unattached.

09:10.767 --> 09:13.988
Yeah. Catch him between
disappointments.

09:14.075 --> 09:15.772
I got this.

09:15.859 --> 09:17.948
I know he's not the kind of guy
you usually go out with

09:18.035 --> 09:19.646
