No, she's a stone-cold fox.

11:59.327 --> 12:02.373
Just be yourself with Victoria,
and everything will be fine.

12:02.460 --> 12:04.636
Be myself?
I'm a socially awkward fat man

12:04.724 --> 12:06.813
who has a tendency
to talk too much!

12:06.900 --> 12:09.076
So you are aware
of the talking thing?

12:10.468 --> 12:11.861
Yeah, you shouldn't
talk at all.

12:11.948 --> 12:13.254
