silent type

12:13.341 --> 12:15.560
like Harrison Ford
or Clint Eastwood.

12:15.647 --> 12:17.040
There you go,
just pick a movie star

12:17.127 --> 12:19.129
and try to emulate them.

12:19.216 --> 12:22.742
I certainly love
Olympia Dukakis.

12:22.829 --> 12:24.221
Alright, let's see
if we can't turn

12:24.308 --> 12:26.571
our portly duckling
into a sexy swan.

12:26.658 --> 12:28.573
